  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hannah is a surreal 3D platformer about childhood trauma, 80s-inspired horror, and broken memories. Explore, feel, and choose your path across a VHS-styled dreamworld with multiple endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466870/extras/77c95387213bee8f94514f307ce958e4.poster.avif?t=1772232903\" width=748 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466870/extras/77c95387213bee8f94514f307ce958e4.webm?t=1772232903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466870/extras/77c95387213bee8f94514f307ce958e4.mp4?t=1772232903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A journey through childhood nightmares</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hannah has lost her favorite doll and now has to face a surreal and enigmatic world shaped by her own mind and her memories of the 1980s, a world where every shadow hides a secret.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466870/extras/0808e6c90c3cd3498c9197072cee130f.poster.avif?t=1772232903\" width=750 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466870/extras/0808e6c90c3cd3498c9197072cee130f.webm?t=1772232903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466870/extras/0808e6c90c3cd3498c9197072cee130f.mp4?t=1772232903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this atmospheric 3D puzzle-platformer, you must explore mysterious settings, solve intriguing challenges, and confront your worst childhood fears in an immersive and unforgettable experience where every decision determines the ending of the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466870/extras/a846bca06d275e0f28f4359f240760a9.poster.avif?t=1772232903\" width=750 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466870/extras/a846bca06d275e0f28f4359f240760a9.webm?t=1772232903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466870/extras/a846bca06d275e0f28f4359f240760a9.mp4?t=1772232903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore the dark side of your mind</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From narrow paths to vast surreal landscapes, each environment tells a visually stunning story.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An ever-changing environment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game adapts to player's choice, altering the environment and influencing the ending.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve challenging puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use logic and creativity to overcome obstacles and unravel the path ahead bringing you closer to understanding yourself.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A deep and interpretive narrative</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find objects that tell your story, clues that reveal fragments of your past. A story of self-discovery that unfolds as you explore.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Soundtrack composed by a Grammy winner</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The music and sound effects created especially for the game completely envelop you, creating an extraordinary, immersive, and emotional experience.</p>",
